cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with video object segmentation using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) category. The use of offline and online learning strategies also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The incorporation of multiple annotated frames and the ability to handle different types of input annotations indicate a potential overlap with multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
